<L>__{exterior motel night}
<A>__{louis, having just thrown on some pants, walks outside his room and sees ordell's big, black oldsmobile parked in front of the motel. as he approaches, the power window on the driver's side comes down, revealing a comfortable ordell sitting back in his seat looking up at louis.}
