<D>__{he put himself in a situation where he was gonna have to do ten years in the penetentiary, that's what he did.}
<P>__{(taking out a viceroy and lighting it up)}
<D>__{and if you know beaumont, you know there aint no way in hell he can do no ten years. and if you know that, you know beaumont's gonna go any goddam thing beaumont can to keep from doin' those ten years including telling the federal government everything they want to know about my ass. now that, my friend, is a clear case of him or me. and you best believe it aint gonna be me. you know what i'm sayin'? you gonna come in on this with me, you gotta be prepared to go all the way. i got me so far over a half a million dollars sittin' in lockboxes in a bank in cabo san lucas. me and mr. walker make us one more delivery, i'm gonna have me over a million. you think i'm gonna let this little cheese eatin' nigga here fuck that up? shit, you better think again. 'fore i let this deal get fucked up, i will shoot that nigga in the head, and ten niggas look just like em.}
